social_posts.post_text: As 2022 is wrapping up, wanted to recap on some of the highlights this year. Started off the year with having some of my work instores + on a store front!! Got out of my comfort zone and was interviewed by @other.scene. Also, got the opportunity to work with one of my dream clients, @nike! So grateful for each + every opportunity and to all the new creatives I met this year! Looking forward to 2023 🖤
A couple weeks ago, I proposed to my best friend! I can’t wait to spend the rest of my life with you @denneserodriguez ❤️❤️❤️
